#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.dtype.metadata:4
msgid ""
"The metadata field can be set using any dictionary at data-type creation. "
"NumPy currently has no uniform approach to propagating metadata; although "
"some array operations preserve it, there is no guarantee that others will."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.dtype.metadata:11
msgid ""
"Although used in certain projects, this feature was long undocumented and is "
"not well supported. Some aspects of metadata propagation are expected to "
"change in the future."
msgstr ""

